summary: This memorandum concerns U.S. contacts for a resistance group in Cuba, specifically the Unidad de Liberacion Nacional (ULN), and their plans to overthrow Castro. It details principle players, including AMCANOE-1 through AMCANOE-9, and reviews files related to efforts to unify exiles and support for Castro's overthrow, including an offer by the Cosa Nostra to assassinate Castro.
title: AMCANOE
